    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2000-07-27", 
    "text": "Long-Term Caregivers Assistance Act of 2000 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow an annual income-based, long-term care credit of $2,000 times the number of eligible persons for whom a taxpayer is a qualifying caregiver.Prohibits a credit allowance for less than the full tax year, except in the case of a taxpayer's death."
